                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-34-off189 t17980912-34-cd190"></join>, an iron coulter, value 3s. two iron tucks, value 12d. two iron keys, value 2d. and two iron bolts, value 6d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17980912-34-victim370" type="victimName">
